《'''''Mycelium Running: How Mushrooms Can Help Save the World'''''》是美國[[真菌學|真菌學家]][[保羅·史塔曼茲|保羅·史塔曼茲]]的第六本著作，由{{link-en|Ten Speed Press|Ten Speed Press}}在2005年出版。

在本書中，史塔曼茲主要探討將[[真菌|真菌]]應用在[[生物修復|生物修復]]--即[[真菌修復|真菌修復]]的方法，他詳細描述了以無毒的[[菌絲體|菌絲體]]抑制[[螞蟻|螞蟻]]、[[白蟻|白蟻]]等昆蟲的方法，甚至還可利用真菌治療[[炭疽病|炭疽病]]、[[天花|天花]]或中和[[神經毒素|神經毒素]]<ref>{{cite journal |author=Starhawk |authorlink=Starhawk |year=2006 |title=Notes from Underground – Book review: ''Mycelium Running: How Mushrooms Can Help Save the World'' |journal=[[Yes!_(U.S._magazine)|Yes!]] |issue=38 |publisher=Positive Futures Network |url=http://www.yesmagazine.org/issues/5000-years-of-empire/notes-from-underground |issn=1089-6651 |accessdate=1 January 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029185431/http://www.yesmagazine.org/issues/5000-years-of-empire/notes-from-underground |archive-date=2013-10-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Magic Mushrooms: That fungus among us is good for more than just eating |first=Kelly |last=Hearn |url=http://www.metroactive.com/papers/sonoma/09.22.04/dining-0439.html |newspaper=[[North_Bay_Bohemian|North Bay Bohemian]] |date=22 September 2004 |issn=1532-0154 |accessdate=1 January 2013 |archive-date=2019-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915064525/http://www.metroactive.com/papers/sonoma/09.22.04/dining-0439.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

